Wellness Center

Wellness Center Hours

507 Willow Grove Road

Centerville, IN 47330

Questions?

Ryan Cole Wellness Center Coordinator

rcole@centerville.k12.in.us

Phone: (765) 855-3481 x2097

Emergency Contact: (317) 679-0104

If you would like to speak with a staff member personally, please call during Wellness Center hours.

About the Wellness Center

The Centerville Wellness Center is located at the Centerville High School campus and is open to the general public. Benefits of having a membership include:

Inexpensive fees for single and family packages and discounts for senior citizens

Hammer Strength weight equipment

Trainers available to help design your personal workout plan

Locker and shower provided

Free weights and track

The Wellness Center features Hammer Strength weight equipment and more than 14 cardiovascular machines including:

4 elliptical machines

3 spinning bikes

2 recumbent bikes

5 treadmills

Fees

Notes

Any certified or non-certified personnel currently employed by the Centerville-Abington Community Schools is entitled to free membership.

Any student currently enrolled in an educational facility: student I.D. must be presented.

Children up to the age of 14 must be accompanied by an adult.
